manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "Raffle_MongoDB_API"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "Raffle_MongoDB_API"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
actix-files = "0.6"
actix-web-httpauth = "0.6"
bson = "2.1"
config = "0.12"
confy = "0.4.0"
env_logger = "0.9"
futures = "0.3.2"
glob = "0.3"
json = "0.12.4"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
log = "0.4.1"
mongodb = "2.1.0"
reqwest = "0.11.9"
rust_decimal = "1.22.0"
rustls = "0.20.2"
rustls-pemfile = "0.2.1"
snafu = "0.7"

[dependencies.actix-web]
version = "4.0"
features = ["rustls"]
optional = false

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.19"
features = ["serde"]
optional = false

[dependencies.openssl]
version = "0.10"
features = ["vendored"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false
